Goal

Collect a valid search origin and search radius to match the Repair Request to Shops, with minimal friction and clear user understanding.

Definitions

Location: a geo point (lat/lng) + human-readable label (city or address).

Radius: numeric kilometers used for matching.

Screen behavior (Step 3: Location)
1) Location input (required)

User must provide location via one of:

Use current location (device geolocation)

Search input (autocomplete) that accepts:

City (e.g., “Kraków”)

Address (e.g., “Grunwaldzka 10, Gdańsk”)

UI requirements

Show a single prominent field: City or address

Show a clear secondary button: Use current location

Validation

“Continue/Submit” must be disabled until location is resolved to a geo point.

2) Map preview (appears after location is set)

Once location is resolved:

Display a map with a pin at the resolved point.

Allow user to adjust location by:

dragging the pin, or

clicking “Adjust on map” which opens map interaction mode.

Copy

If only city is entered: “Pin is set to the city center. Add street for more accuracy.”

3) Radius control (hidden until location is set)

Before location is set:

Radius UI is hidden or disabled with a hint: “Choose location to set radius”.

After location is set:

Show radius section:

Search radius: 15 km (value visible)

slider (or +/- buttons) controlling radius

map draws a circle around the pin representing the radius

Radius constraints

Min/max configurable.

User can set with:

slider + numeric label (mandatory)

optional: make numeric label editable

4) Submission

CTA label: consistent with your chosen term (either “Wyślij zlecenie” or “Wyślij zgłoszenie”).

When submitting:

show loading state

handle errors (geolocation denied, autocomplete failure)

States to implement

Empty: no location selected

show input + “Use current location”

hide radius + map

Resolving: user selected suggestion / geolocation in progress

loading indicator in field/button

Location set: pin + map visible, radius UI visible, circle drawn

Location adjusted: user moved pin

update label to “Custom location” (or keep city name + “adjusted”)

Error:

Geolocation denied → “Allow location or type a city”

Autocomplete no results → “Try city + voivodeship” / “Check spelling”

Map API down (if applicable) → fallback to city input + radius slider without map